com.yahoo.document

Class DataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.vespa.objects.Selectable
      • com.yahoo.vespa.objects.Identifiable
        • com.yahoo.document.DataType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<DataType>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotationReferenceDataType, CollectionDataType, MapDataType, PrimitiveDataType, ReferenceDataType, StructuredDataType, TensorDataType

    public abstract class DataType
extends Identifiable
implements Serializable, Comparable<DataType>
    Enumeration of the possible types of fields. Since arrays and weighted sets may be defined for any types, including themselves, this enumeration is open ended.
    Author:
    bratseth
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
